How teams in the Alabama Sports Writers Association rankings fared this week: 
CLASS 7A 
1. Bob Jones (7-0) beat Grissom 37-0 
2. Spain Park (6-1) beat Vestavia Hills 21-0 
3. James Clemens (6-1) beat Gadsden City 13-7 
4. Prattville (5-2) lost to Enterprise 28-20 
5. Hoover (6-1) beat Tuscaloosa Co. 45-3 
6. Central-Phenix City (6-2) beat Triple A Focus Aca. (Texas) 49-0 
7. Theodore (6-1) did not play 
8. Murphy (5-2) beat Foley 37-17 on Thursday 
9. Buckhorn (5-2) beat Sparkman 60-28 on Thursday 
10. McGill-Toolen (6-1) beat Davidson 24-0 
CLASS 6A 
1. Clay-Chalkville (7-0) beat Shades Valley 52-7 
2. Spanish Fort (7-0) beat No. 8 Blount 41-38 
3. Opelika (8-0) beet Valley 71-0 
4. Muscle Shoals (8-0) beat Decatur 28-0 
5. Saraland (6-1) beat Baldwin Co. 56-35 
6. Benjamin Russell (7-1) beat Chelsea 42-25 on Thursday 
7. McAdory (6-1) beat Hillcrest-Tuscaloosa 35-14 
8. Blount (6-1) lost to No. 2 Spanish Fort 41-38 
9. Homewood (5-2) lost to Walker 17-14 
10. Park Crossing (7-1) beat Carver-Montgomery 48-27
